snippet.title: Political Animals Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: First teaser trailer for the upcoming 2016 Political Strategy game 'Political Animals' www.politicalanimalsgame.com Developed by Squeaky Wheel and published by Positech Games. Are you a corrupt crocodile or a meritocratic mouse? and can you win the election without resorting to bribes and corruption?
